  "title": "Outsourced Finance Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>-Maintain full sets of accounts for a portfolio of clients.</p><p>-Prepare consolidated management accounts and group financial statements.</p><p>-Prepare statutory financial statements in accordance with applicable financial reporting standards and disclosure requirements.</p><p>-Prepare and submit XBRL report in compliance with regulatory requirements.</p><p>-Maintain proper documentation and working papers for review and regulatory compliance.</p><p>-Any other administrative support for the function.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>-Bachelor's degree in Accounting/ Finance or equivalent professional qualification.</p><p>-Minimum 2 years relevant experience in accounting related role.</p><p>-Proficient with Accounting Software such as Quickbooks and Xero.</p><p>-Knowledge of International Financial Reporting Standards, Singapore Financial Reporting Standards and relevant statutory and regulatory requirements.</p><p>-Self-starter, organized, attention to detail, deadline oriented, and able to work independently in a fast-paced environment.</p>",
