    "uen": "201510979W",
    "description": "<p>RT Advisory Pte Ltd &amp; RT Group of Companies (RT or RT Group) which founded the RT ASEAN Network continues to push boundaries to provide innovative solutions to refine traditional service offerings in the areas of statutory compliance and business advisory. Driven by its core strategy of Internationalisation, Innovation, and Integration, RT focuses on providing clients with seamless services across professional disciplines and jurisdictions.</p>\n<p>Headquartered in Singapore, the clientele base of RT Group spans across the globe, ranging from small businesses to multi-national companies. From listed organisations in SGX and stock exchanges in other jurisdictions, non-listed corporates, financial institutions, charities, societies, to partnerships, RT continues to provide our relevant and effective services to our clients across different industries and sectors.</p>\n<p>RT and RT ASEAN network are the first of its kind with access to multi-disciplinary experts and has access to multi-jurisdictional presence in over 16 countries. The RT tagline: ONE FACE ACROSS ASEAN emphasises its aspiration to represent clients’ interests across jurisdictions in a seamless manner.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>At RT, we are looking for people who share a similar vision of Leadership, Commitment &amp; Trustworthiness. If you share these values, and are looking to be part of an innovative and boundary-breaking team, apply to us today.</strong></p>",
